Type Command means Add Command or Done Command or Quit Command

Record Add Command
  Has Title as String

Record Done Command
  Has Id as Int

Record Quit Command

Make Command be New Add Command with Title be "ship language" as Command

Make Message be Match Command
  When Add Command with Title be Title
    "add {Title}"
  When Done Command named Done
    "done {Id of Done}"
  When Quit Command
    "quit"

Say Message
